トピック.授業外学習2:
Students are expected to complete reading assignments on
time to prepare for classes. <br /><p class="MsoNormal">Attendance is mandatory. In the event of illness or other absence, please
notify your instructor. <br />
Students are required to leave comments/questions/impressions regarding class
material in the respective discussion forums on LUNA (counts as class
participation 30%). <br />
All students are also required to participate in a field trip to observe a performance of kabuki, bunraku or noh, and to
submit a short response paper on their experience.<br />
Students will be given extra credit for attending individually other performances
in the Kansai area and can write the response paper on those performances.</p>





